# Summary

| Step | Method | Status |
|------|--------|--------|
| CFA | 2-factor model, lavaan MLR | ✅ Fit criteria met |
| Mixture Model | 3-component (target + swap + guess) | ✅ Converged |
| H2a (κ ~ Eff × Dist) | Linear regression on ML estimates | ✅ Interaction tested |
| H2b (p_swap ~ Eff × Dist) | Linear regression on ML estimates | ✅ Interaction tested |

Note: For the actual study, the ML mixture model will be replaced with Bayesian estimation via the `bmm` package (built on `brms`/Stan), which provides posterior distributions, credible intervals, and Bayes factors for hypothesis testing.

